CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. B10 reads: "Chi Delta Mu Fraternity Entertains Lavishly - Chi Delta Mu Officers are, left to right, Dr. Charles Burks, Dr. W.A. Harris, Dr. Robert Bolden, Dr. Paul Knott, Dr. Garfield Nickens and Dr. Arthur Henderson." Portion of accompanying article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. A7 by Toki Schalk Johnson reads:"Wednesday brought forth the annual dinner dance given by the Chi Delta Mu Fraternity in beautifully decorated New Arena."
